def-en: The the context of mathematics, the process relating to finding a linear equation that accurately describes the numerical patterns in a data set.
def-ga: I gcomhthéacs matamaitice, an próiseas a bhaineann le cothromóid líne a fháil a dhéanann cur síos cruinn ar patrúin uimhriúla i sraith sonraí.
notes: Luann an trí fhoinse thuas an téarma seo sa gcomhthéacs ceannann céanna; .i. mar théarma matamaitice.
